00:12:07,450 --> 00:12:08,450
你好吗
Hi there!

201
00:12:08,620 --> 00:12:11,230
您的小胡子不错啊
Love your moustache, monsieur!

202
00:12:11,480 --> 00:12:13,290
啊 这就是巴黎
Ah, yes, Paris!

203
00:12:13,440 --> 00:12:16,010
这里有浪漫 这里有梦想
City of romance. City of dreams.

204
00:12:16,040 --> 00:12:18,200
这里有名望与财富
City of fame and fortune!

205
00:12:18,650 --> 00:12:22,800
还有 路灯和鸽子
City of lamp posts. City of pigeons.

206
00:12:22,970 --> 00:12:24,320
浪漫说过了吗
Did I say romance?

207
00:12:24,560 --> 00:12:26,570
是的 说过了 那舞蹈学校在哪儿呢
Yes, you did. Now, where's the dance school?

208
00:12:26,670 --> 00:12:29,370
呃…我不知道
Uh, I don't know.

209
00:12:30,360 --> 00:12:32,240
没关系 我们是伙伴
Don't worry. We're a team.

210
00:12:32,650 --> 00:12:33,880
我们一起去找
We'll find it together.

211
00:12:33,960 --> 00:12:34,800
呃
Ugh!

212
00:12:36,330 --> 00:12:38,480
你不觉得这样逃出来有点太鲁莽了
Do you think it was stupid to come to Paris?

213
00:12:38,500 --> 00:12:41,880
别这样说 我们可不能因为这点小事就轻言放弃
Don't say that! We should never give up on our dreams.

214
00:12:45,360 --> 00:12:47,500
可我们只是孤儿 对巴黎一无所知
We're kids! We're all alone.

215
00:12:48,650 --> 00:12:51,150
或许我梦想成为舞蹈家 真的是异想天开呢
Was I really crazy to think I could be a dancer?

216
00:12:51,690 --> 00:12:52,700
你觉得呢
What do you think?

217
00:12:54,480 --> 00:12:55,120
维克多？
Victor?

218
00:12:56,520 --> 00:12:57,280
唉我说
I said...

219
00:12:58,540 --> 00:12:59,160
维克多？
Victor?

220
00:13:00,090 --> 00:13:01,340
我没事
I'm OK!

221
00:13:01,690 --> 00:13:02,600
你去那做什么 快回来
Come back!

222
00:13:02,640 --> 00:13:04,210
可我不会游泳
I can't swim!

223
00:13:04,780 --> 00:13:07,900
明早七点 在这座桥上等我 我们不见不散
Meet me on this bridge at this time tomorrow.

224
00:13:08,190 --> 00:13:10,090
无论遇到什么情况
No matter how dangerous it is,

225
00:13:10,400 --> 00:13:13,180
我一定会到的
I will return!

226
00:13:14,840 --> 00:13:15,920
维克多
Victor!

227
00:13:16,670 --> 00:13:17,910
你快回来
Come back!

228
00:13:18,620 --> 00:13:20,080
别丢下我
Don't leave!

229
00:13:21,610 --> 00:13:22,810
求你了
Please.

230
00:13:36,830 --> 00:13:37,710
嗯
Huh?

231
00:14:41,100 --> 00:14:43,180
[每个女生都值得拥有一套宝诗龙首饰]

232
00:15:43,000 --> 00:15:43,630
嗷
Aaah!

233
00:15:45,080 --> 00:15:47,040
给我老实交代
What have you come here to do, huh?

234
00:15:47,080 --> 00:15:48,830
你来这儿想偷什么
You came here to steal, didn't you?

235
00:15:49,180 --> 00:15:50,720
告诉我 你这个贼
Answer me! You're a thief!

236
00:15:50,790 --> 00:15:54,280
我没想偷东西 我只是在看她跳舞
I wasn't stealing! I was looking at the dancer!

237
00:15:54,380 --> 00:15:56,460
别想撒谎 把东西拿出来
Liar! Empty your pockets!

238
00:15:56,520 --> 00:15:57,600
放开我
Get off me!

239
00:15:57,630 --> 00:15:59,200
你想得美
Oh, yeah?

240
00:15:59,230 --> 00:16:00,460
住手 放开她
Leave her alone.

241
00:16:01,160 --> 00:16:02,510
她是个小偷
She came here to steal!

242
00:16:02,540 --> 00:16:05,680
我不是 我没有偷东西
I didn't! I really didn't!

243
00:16:05,950 --> 00:16:07,040
先想清楚
Think this through.

244
00:16:07,610 --> 00:16:10,250
如果你指认她是小偷 那你得向院长解释一下
If you hurt her, then you will have to explain

245
00:16:10,320 --> 00:16:12,200
她是怎么溜进来的
how she got here in the first place,

246
00:16:13,360 --> 00:16:16,280
而你 守门人 那时到哪里去了
and aren't you supposed to be taking care of the building?

247
00:16:16,830 --> 00:16:19,100
D你能承担起这个责任吗
o you really want to take the fall for this?

248
00:16:27,960 --> 00:16:28,910
别挡路
Clear off.

249
00:16:32,160 --> 00:16:32,840
等一下
Wait!

250
00:16:32,920 --> 00:16:34,240
快走吧 离开这里
Go. Get out of here.

251
00:17:02,880 --> 00:17:04,940
我可没什么让你偷
I have nothing to steal!

252
00:17:05,310 --> 00:17:07,590
我这样 说不出话来
I-I can't sp... I can't speak!

253
00:17:07,750 --> 00:17:10,250
我只是想说 谢谢你救我一命
I just wanted to say thank you for saving me!

254
00:17:10,410 --> 00:17:12,080
你谢过了 好自为之吧
You've said it. Have a nice life.

255
00:17:17,530 --> 00:17:20,700
请问 刚才跳舞的人是谁啊
Excuse me, but who was that dancer on stage?

256
00:17:20,970 --> 00:17:23,260
罗西塔莫里 芭蕾舞明星
Rosita Mauri, top dancer at the Opera.

257
00:17:23,310 --> 00:17:23,870
哇
Wow!

258
00:17:24,040 --> 00:17:28,200
刚才她做出的那个惊人的跳跃 这是太美了
And what she did - that crazy jumpy thing, what was that?

259
00:17:29,160 --> 00:17:30,280
你也是个舞蹈演员吗？
Are you a dancer too?

260
00:17:30,410 --> 00:17:32,910
我只是个清洁工 你真的有点烦
I'm a cleaner, and you are an irritation.

261
00:17:32,960 --> 00:17:33,720
别再跟着我了
Go away.

262
00:17:36,670 --> 00:17:37,560
可您是在这儿第一个
But you're the first person

263
00:17:37,630 --> 00:17:39,740
对我这么好的人
to show me any kindness in this city.

264
00:17:40,410 --> 00:17:42,680
我和同伴走丢了
I've been separated from my best friend.

265
00:17:43,530 --> 00:17:45,020
我现在无家可归
I have nowhere to go,

266
00:17:45,980 --> 00:17:47,260
而且我是个孤儿 拜托
and I'm an orphan.

267
00:17:47,710 --> 00:17:50,500
是很可怜 可我讨厌小孩儿
Nice try, but I hate kids,

268
00:17:51,020 --> 00:17:52,660
尤其是孤儿
especially orphans.

269
00:17:53,080 --> 00:17:54,700
给我让开
Go find another idiot.

270
00:18:06,250 --> 00:18:08,320
擦楼梯去 奥黛特
The stairs, Odette.

271
00:18:08,400 --> 00:18:09,950
它们脏兮兮的 丢我的脸
The stairs are a disgrace.

272
00:18:10,350 --> 00:18:11,690
明天还有客人来呢
I have guests tomorrow afternoon,

273
00:18:11,740 --> 00:18:15,200
我要你把房子彻底打扫得焕然一新 听见了吗
and I want my building looking worthy top to bottom.

274
00:18:15,980 --> 00:18:17,200
是的 夫人
I understand, ma'am.

275
00:18:17,770 --> 00:18:19,630
既然你听清了
If you understand,

276
00:18:19,680 --> 00:18:21,640
打扫干净之前不准休息
why are you entering your rooms?

277
00:18:33,480 --> 00:18:34,460
我来帮您吧
Let me help you!

278
00:18:34,760 --> 00:18:35,820
别碍事
Get out of here!

279
00:18:36,750 --> 00:18:39,550
但您需要我 帮您打扫
You need me. I can clean.

280
00:18:39,770 --> 00:18:42,380
我可以打扫得非常干净
In fact, 'Squeaky Clean' is my middle name.

281
00:18:42,540 --> 00:18:44,780
我还年轻 腿脚灵活 不像您一样…
I'm young. My legs work. Yours don't.

282
00:18:46,120 --> 00:18:49,360
呃我是说 我可以帮您非常轻松地完成工作啊
Uh, it's gonna feel so much easier with me helping.

283
00:18:59,320 --> 00:19:00,540
还要我请你进来吗
Are you coming?

284
00:19:02,830 --> 00:19:04,780
哇 这儿台阶真多
Whoa! That's a lot of stairs.

285
00:19:06,620 --> 00:19:07,850
您在这里工作吗
Are you the caretaker?

286
00:19:07,920 --> 00:19:11,440
是的 你在能够独立生活之前 可以暂住在我这里
Yes. And you can stay with me until you get on your feet,

287
00:19:11,630 --> 00:19:15,260
但有个条件 别再问问题了
On one condition -no more questions.

288
00:19:15,320 --> 00:19:15,960
那我可以住多久呢
How long can I stay?

289
00:19:16,300 --> 00:19:18,110
又来 问个没完
Ugh. That was a question.

290
00:19:18,160 --> 00:19:20,460
对了 刚才那位很凶的夫人是谁啊
By the way, who was that witch?

291
00:19:20,620 --> 00:19:23,200
雷吉纳勒奥 这座房子的主人
Regine Le Haut. She owns this building.

292
00:19:23,520 --> 00:19:26,380
她就喜欢吃你这种红头发马尾辫的小女孩儿
And she eats ginger orphans with ponytails.

293
00:19:27,070 --> 00:19:27,920
快干活吧
Now, clean!

294
00:19:28,160 --> 00:19:28,880
哈哈
Ha!

295
00:19:30,430 --> 00:19:31,070
嗯？
Huh?

296
00:19:32,170 --> 00:19:33,050
您在这工作多久了
How long have you worked here?

297
00:19:33,080 --> 00:19:35,000
我该怎么称呼您呢 您有绰号吗 我有个绰号 您想听吗
Do you have a nickname? Wanna know mine?

298
00:19:35,000 --> 00:19:35,980
我有单人床睡吗
Will I have my own bed?

299
00:19:36,620 --> 00:19:38,540
您夜里不打呼噜的吧 您起床早吗
Do you snore? Are you a morning person?

300
00:19:38,560 --> 00:19:39,530
您最喜欢什么水果啊
What's your favourite fruit?

301
00:19:39,600 --> 00:19:41,990
我们早餐吃什么啊 我喜欢面包配果酱
What do you have for breakfast? I love baguette and jam.

302
00:19:42,160 --> 00:19:45,290
您知道吗 我是因为想跳舞才逃出了孤儿院
You know I escaped from the orphanage to become a pupil at the Opera.

303
00:19:45,440 --> 00:19:46,060
真的吗？
Did you?

304
00:19:46,160 --> 00:19:48,620
您在那儿工作 应该也有认识的人吧
You work there, so you must know people.

305
00:19:49,180 --> 00:19:50,040
您能帮帮我吗
Could you help me?

306
00:19:50,320 --> 00:19:51,370
你可别指望我
Don't hold your breath.

307
00:19:51,630 --> 00:19:55,500
昨晚那支舞真是太美了
What that étoile did yesterday,oh, it was so magical.

308
00:19:56,010 --> 00:19:58,990
我喜欢跳舞 您也会跳舞吗
I love dancing. Do you love dancing?

309
00:20:00,240 --> 00:20:01,840
是因为你脚瘸了吗
Is that because you've got a limp?

310
00:20:03,960 --> 00:20:04,520
起来
Get up

311
00:20:04,920 --> 00:20:05,560
是的 夫人
Yes, ma'am.

312
00:20:05,680 --> 00:20:06,510
她是谁
Who is this?

313
00:20:06,860 --> 00:20:08,810
谁也不是 她来帮忙的
No-one. She helps.

314
00:20:08,910 --> 00:20:12,080
那你养她 自己出钱
You feed it out of your wages.

315
00:20:12,190 --> 00:20:12,990
好的 夫人
Yes, ma'am.

316
00:20:13,320 --> 00:20:16,510
我要你把桌布烘干熨好 快去
I want you to air and press the linen. Now!

317
00:20:17,930 --> 00:20:18,910
嗯～
Hmm...

318
00:20:21,320 --> 00:20:22,730
还不够干净
It's not clean.

319
00:20:37,560 --> 00:20:38,540
嗯？
Huh?

320
00:20:59,500 --> 00:20:59,960
喔
Whoa!

321
00:21:01,130 --> 00:21:01,960
喔 哦
Whoa! Oh!

322
00:21:02,400 --> 00:21:02,990
噢
Oh! Whoa!

323
00:21:05,340 --> 00:21:06,370
你好啊
Hello!

324
00:21:08,440 --> 00:21:11,290
不知道仆人进来要先敲门吗 你是谁
Servants are supposed to knock. Who are you?

325
00:21:13,020 --> 00:21:16,300
我叫菲丽西 是来帮奥黛特打扫卫生的
I'm Felicie. I work with Odette. I clean.

326
00:21:16,440 --> 00:21:17,930
♫ 哒哒哒 ♫
♪ Da da da da... ♪

327
00:21:18,080 --> 00:21:20,000
那我先告退了 回头见
OK! I'm done. 'Bye now!

328
00:21:20,040 --> 00:21:23,320
站住 小耗子，你刚刚在偷看 对不对？
Wait, little rat! You were spying, weren't you?

329
00:21:23,370 --> 00:21:24,800
怎么会 我没有
I don't think so.

330
00:21:24,910 --> 00:21:25,950
不 你就是
Yes, you were.

331
00:21:26,080 --> 00:21:29,740
你从没见过如此美丽的舞姿才会偷看的
You were admiring the most wonderful dancer you've ever seen.

332
00:21:29,910 --> 00:21:31,450
是不是这样 小耗子
Isn't that so, little rat?

333
00:21:31,530 --> 00:21:34,410
别说了 你还不是最棒的舞者
You're not THE most wonderful dancer.

334
00:21:34,640 --> 00:21:35,550
昨天晚上我看到的…
Yesterday I saw...

335
00:21:35,600 --> 00:21:36,590
不得无礼
Don't be insolent!

336
00:21:40,640 --> 00:21:41,950
你也是芭蕾舞演员吗
Are you a ballet dancer?

337
00:21:42,000 --> 00:21:42,970
现在还不是 不过很快就是
I will be.

338
00:21:43,080 --> 00:21:44,200
我和妈妈正等着
 Mother and I are waiting

339
00:21:44,270 --> 00:21:46,480
巴黎歌剧院寄来的录取通知书呢
for the letter that admits me to the Opera.

340
00:21:46,710 --> 00:21:49,120
我很有天赋
I am so talented!

341
00:21:49,260 --> 00:21:52,090
院长非常喜欢去我们家的餐厅用餐
Plus the director dines in my mom's restaurant,

342
00:21:52,200 --> 00:21:54,350
因为那里有全巴黎最好吃的牛肋排
and he loves the prime rib.

343
00:21:55,790 --> 00:22:00,780
很快 我就会成为全巴黎最有名的芭蕾舞之星
So this time next year, I shall be a famous ballerina.

344
00:22:00,860 --> 00:22:03,290
芭蕾舞明星 真棒啊 那也是我的梦想
Ballerina! Me too!

345
00:22:03,390 --> 00:22:06,330
来照照镜子 小耗子
Ha Reality check, little rat!

346
00:22:06,640 --> 00:22:09,960
你没戏 只有我才能成为明星
You're nothing. I'm a star!

347
00:22:10,160 --> 00:22:12,460
而你只配绕着我转
You're just orbiting around me.

348
00:22:13,130 --> 00:22:13,800
那是什么？
What's that?

349
00:22:14,000 --> 00:22:15,720
你是不是偷了我们家的东西
Have you stolen something from me?

350
00:22:15,790 --> 00:22:16,240
没有啊
No.

351
00:22:16,330 --> 00:22:18,080
给我看看
Show me! What is it?

352
00:22:18,080 --> 00:22:20,460
那是妈妈留给我的音乐盒 非常珍贵
It's mine, and it's precious.

353
00:22:21,370 --> 00:22:22,270
哦
Oh!

354
00:22:26,270 --> 00:22:27,230
是啊
I'm sure.

355
00:22:28,010 --> 00:22:28,810
那你去捡吧
Fetch!

356
00:22:29,060 --> 00:22:31,040
不要
No!

357
00:22:37,600 --> 00:22:38,320
哦 不
Oops!

358
00:22:41,710 --> 00:22:42,590
哦
Oh!

359
00:22:45,020 --> 00:22:46,040
哦
Oh!

360
00:22:56,080 --> 00:23:00,270
从歌剧院寄来的雷吉纳勒奥夫人和卡米儿小姐的信件
A letter for Madame Regine Le Haut and Mademoiselle Camille from the Opera.

361
00:23:00,350 --> 00:23:04,620
让我闻闻 信纸真香 带印花 蓝墨水儿
Hmm! Handmade paper! Embossed! Blue ink!

362
00:23:05,260 --> 00:23:08,680
现在的小孩儿真没教养 哼
Oh, how rude! Children today have no manners!

363
00:23:11,600 --> 00:23:12,470
[录取信 致卡米尔小姐]

364
00:23:28,400 --> 00:23:29,320
把它拿来
Give me that!

365
00:23:31,640 --> 00:23:33,840
你才不是卡米尔勒奥
You are not Camille Le Haut!

366
00:23:33,950 --> 00:23:34,730
我就是啊
Of course I am.

367
00:23:34,780 --> 00:23:35,360
又想骗我
No, you're not!

368
00:23:35,790 --> 00:23:37,490
我看你这次想去警局
This time I call the police!

369
00:23:37,660 --> 00:23:40,140
警局？ 我不要去警局 放开我
Police? Police? Why? No!

370
00:23:40,170 --> 00:23:44,120
♫ 啦啦啦 ♫
♪ La la la la... ♪

371
00:23:44,160 --> 00:23:45,370
出什么事了
What's going on here?

372
00:23:45,440 --> 00:23:48,540
院长先生 她自称是卡米尔勒奥
Um, she says she's Camille Le Haut.

373
00:23:48,640 --> 00:23:51,780
我看看 你说你是卡米尔勒奥吗
Hmm... Are you Camille Le Haut?

374
00:23:51,960 --> 00:23:54,090
嗯…没错
Uh... yes?

375
00:23:54,410 --> 00:23:58,560
哈哈哈 她就是卡米尔勒奥
Hmm...She IS Camille Le Haut!

376
00:23:59,340 --> 00:24:01,310
做的不错 这没你什么事了 去干活吧
Return to your post, my friend.

377
00:24:01,320 --> 00:24:02,940
好吧 我不管了
Alright, please yourselves.

378
00:24:02,970 --> 00:24:06,210
幸会 勒奥小姐
Welcome, Miss Le Haut! Charmed!

379
00:24:07,080 --> 00:24:08,400
幸会
Charmed!

380
00:24:08,510 --> 00:24:11,080
我叫奥古斯特沃克贝伊
I am Auguste Emmanuel Vaucorbeil,

381
00:24:11,120 --> 00:24:12,990
这所歌剧院的负责人
director of the Opera.

382
00:24:13,310 --> 00:24:15,740
录取你是因为你妈妈的餐厅
You are here because your mother serves

383
00:24:15,840 --> 00:24:17,880
有全巴黎最好吃的牛肋排
the best prime rib in Paris.

384
00:24:18,270 --> 00:24:21,310
噢 希望你的舞姿也一样美
Oh! I hope you dance as well.

385
00:24:21,960 --> 00:24:22,580
那当然了
Of course.

386
00:24:22,880 --> 00:24:24,400
♫ 我至今都梦想 ♫
