Dreams can come true!

754
00:43:39,480 --> 00:43:42,010
哦…噢…哦不
Oh! Oh! Oh no!

755
00:43:47,920 --> 00:43:49,260
一位…二位
First position, second,

756
00:43:49,340 --> 00:43:51,040
三位…四位…五位
third, fourth, fifth.

757
00:43:51,210 --> 00:43:54,010
这五种站法就是一切的基础
These five positions form the basis of everything.

758
00:43:54,110 --> 00:43:57,450
一位 二位 三位 四位 五位
First position, second, third, fourth, fifth.

759
00:43:57,520 --> 00:43:58,380
小跳
Now you jump.

760
00:43:58,670 --> 00:44:01,440
一位 二位 三位 四位 五位
First position, second, third, fourth, fifth.

761
00:44:01,560 --> 00:44:04,000
保持住 微笑
And pose and smile!

762
00:44:05,280 --> 00:44:07,920
如果你感到累了 那说明你有进步
It's when you're tired that you start to progress.

763
00:44:08,080 --> 00:44:11,150
你以前…就是…芭蕾舞演员 是不是？
You were a dancer, weren't you?

764
00:44:12,080 --> 00:44:13,210
不许问东问西
No more questions.

765
00:44:14,170 --> 00:44:14,920
再来
Again!

766
00:44:19,690 --> 00:44:23,310
哎呀呀 够不到吧 你得踮起脚尖才能晾上去
Oh, to reach, you might need to stand on your pointes.

767
00:44:24,590 --> 00:44:26,560
找到那个平衡点
Feel the balance.

768
00:44:28,040 --> 00:44:31,710
你的脚趾 就如柳条般柔美
Your toes must be as flexible as willow

769
00:44:31,920 --> 00:44:34,120
又像顽石般坚韧
and hard as a rock.

770
00:44:37,840 --> 00:44:38,760
一位准备！
First position!

771
00:44:39,340 --> 00:44:43,610
不不不 可不能用手擦
Uh-uh-uh! No hands allowed.

772
00:44:44,240 --> 00:44:44,870
什么
What?

773
00:44:45,880 --> 00:44:47,580
试试…这样擦
Try this way.

774
00:44:47,610 --> 00:44:49,310
疼疼疼 要断了啊～
Oh! Stop! Stop! Oh!

775
00:44:49,500 --> 00:44:51,050
你以前就是练过跳舞 对不对
You were a dancer, weren't you?

776
00:44:51,080 --> 00:44:53,760
你说的没错 满意了吗 小侦探
Of course I was a dancer, Sherlock Holmes.

777
00:44:55,400 --> 00:44:59,250
旋转就是控制眩晕感的方法
To pirouette, you must become the mistress of your dizziness.

778
00:45:00,380 --> 00:45:03,740
你得盯住一个点旋转 别转晕了
Stare at a spot, and don't ever lose it.

779
00:45:06,220 --> 00:45:09,470
好的 现在走向我 别让水洒出来
OK, now come to me, and don't spill the water.

780
00:45:09,480 --> 00:45:10,440
哦～～～
Whoa!

781
00:45:21,290 --> 00:45:22,670
干杯吧 干杯
Cheers! Cheers!

782
00:45:22,970 --> 00:45:26,110
♫ 当你领我纵身一跃 ♫
♪ When you ask me to jump ♪

783
00:45:26,600 --> 00:45:28,620
♫ 我才发觉世间多么广阔 ♫
♪ I say how high... ♪

784
00:45:28,650 --> 00:45:31,500
把你的左脚介绍给你的右脚认识认识
Try to introduce your left foot to your right foot.

785
00:45:31,520 --> 00:45:33,930
让它们今后好好相处吧
See if they can get along one day.

786
00:45:34,140 --> 00:45:37,150
♫ 一切皆在眼前 ♫
♪ I'm waiting in line ♪

787
00:45:38,240 --> 00:45:39,260
♫ 现在轮到我了… ♫
♪ But now that it's time... ♪

788
00:45:39,290 --> 00:45:41,210
我给你指条明路
There's a bright future for you

789
00:45:41,560 --> 00:45:42,990
还是去卖蜡烛吧
as a candle seller.

790
00:45:45,680 --> 00:45:51,420
♫ 现在轮到我了 我将全力以赴 ♫
♪ Now that is my turn I'm gonna take what's mine... ♪

791
00:45:51,450 --> 00:45:52,490
一位
First position!

792
00:45:52,660 --> 00:45:54,700
二位 三位
Second! Third!

793
00:45:55,180 --> 00:45:57,610
四位 五位
Fourth, and rest in fifth.

794
00:45:57,930 --> 00:45:59,870
谢谢 孩子们
Thank you, mam'selles.

795
00:46:08,430 --> 00:46:10,080
你进步很大
That was... better!

796
00:46:11,120 --> 00:46:12,090
谢谢
Thanks!

797
00:46:12,250 --> 00:46:14,400
我觉得我可以做那个惊人的跳跃动作了
I'm ready to do that crazy, jumpy thing.

798
00:46:14,500 --> 00:46:16,600
可不是吗 我也觉得我可以加冕为后了
And I'm the Empress Josephine.

799
00:46:16,620 --> 00:46:17,160
我没在开玩笑啊
I am!

800
00:46:17,200 --> 00:46:18,560
绝对不行
Of course you are,

801
00:46:18,620 --> 00:46:22,120
能做和能做好是两码事
but there's a difference between being ready and being ready to do it well.

802
00:46:22,490 --> 00:46:24,480
我们每天练习就是为了做好它
That's why we train every day.

803
00:46:24,590 --> 00:46:26,080
我们的确每天都有练习啊
That's all we've been doing!

804
00:46:26,140 --> 00:46:28,830
想做那个动作 那你先要面对一个问题
And then you'll be ready when you can answer the question,

805
00:46:28,860 --> 00:46:29,870
你为什么要跳舞呢
"Why do you dance?"

806
00:46:30,090 --> 00:46:32,760
我说过啊 那是我的梦想
I've answered it! It's my dream!

807
00:46:45,610 --> 00:46:46,250
哦
Oh! Oh!

808
00:46:46,940 --> 00:46:48,700
啊～
Ow! Ow!

809
00:46:48,750 --> 00:46:49,420
唉
Oh!

810
00:46:50,440 --> 00:46:54,200
我的小姑娘啊 那个惊人的动作叫做“大跳”
By the way, that crazy jumpy thing is called le grand jeté,

811
00:46:54,910 --> 00:46:55,720
以你现在的水准还欠些火候呢
and you're not ready.

812
00:46:55,760 --> 00:46:58,360
你是在练功夫吗 刚才那一招叫什么
Are you doing dance or kung-fu?

813
00:46:59,340 --> 00:47:01,460
一点儿也不好笑
You are SO funny.

814
00:47:01,870 --> 00:47:04,720
这是维克多 我们一起从孤儿院逃出来的
This is Victor. We escaped from the orphanage together.

815
00:47:04,750 --> 00:47:07,980
贵安 美丽的女士 这套裙衬得您清丽脱俗
Hello! I am loving your apron.

816
00:47:10,490 --> 00:47:12,280
那么说 你们晚上要出去玩咯
It seems that you are going out tonight.

817
00:47:12,290 --> 00:47:12,910
没错
Yep!

818
00:47:13,210 --> 00:47:16,200
她要是回来晚了 我会让你的个头再矮上几寸
Bring her back late and you will be six inches smaller.

819
00:47:16,430 --> 00:47:18,810
我们不会玩太晚的 只是出去随便逛逛
Of course, of course, of course!

820
00:47:18,830 --> 00:47:22,970
绝不沾酒 真的
It's a quiet, sober, quiet, sober thing.

821
00:47:25,260 --> 00:47:27,980
布列塔尼的音乐 太棒了
Breton music?Whoa!

822
00:47:31,720 --> 00:47:33,120
噢 抱歉
Whoa! Excuse me!

823
00:47:42,240 --> 00:47:44,220
我好喜欢这音乐啊
 I love it here! Whoo!

824
00:47:44,220 --> 00:47:45,900
一起跳吧！
Let's party!

825
00:47:49,520 --> 00:47:51,800
你是喜欢这间酒吧 还是喜欢我
Did you say you loved me or the bar?

826
00:47:53,320 --> 00:47:55,160
耶～～～
Yeah! Whoo!

827
00:47:56,220 --> 00:47:57,230
哇
Whoa!

828
00:48:01,640 --> 00:48:02,350
太赞了
Wow!

829
00:48:04,960 --> 00:48:06,010
哇哦
Whoo!

830
00:48:15,600 --> 00:48:17,240
那是我女朋友！
That's my girlfriend!

831
00:48:17,500 --> 00:48:18,730
你可真走运 小子 哈哈
You're a lucky guy!

832
00:48:31,200 --> 00:48:32,600
太美了
Oh, wow!

833
00:48:42,110 --> 00:48:43,400
哦呜
Oh! Oh!

834
00:48:48,200 --> 00:48:51,930
希望明天上课时 你能稍微优雅一点
I hope that tomorrow you act with a little more dignity.

835
00:48:53,600 --> 00:48:58,000
不过今晚的演出…倒是很不错
Anyway, tonight was...a good performance.

836
00:48:58,240 --> 00:48:59,440
谢谢您
Thank you, sir.

837
00:49:01,560 --> 00:49:04,750
啦啦啦
Whoo! Whoo-hoo!

838
00:49:05,790 --> 00:49:09,820
我不知道你为什么这么开心 但是这样很不错
I have no idea why you're happy, but it is great!

839
00:49:18,490 --> 00:49:20,920
好了 我得回去了
Well, I'd better go in.

840
00:49:21,840 --> 00:49:23,200
我明天就可以去测试了
I've got my audition tomorrow.

841
00:49:23,230 --> 00:49:26,060
好极了 那你睡个好觉 我…
Of course! Sleep well. And I... I...

842
00:49:26,600 --> 00:49:27,040
什么？
What?

843
00:49:28,600 --> 00:49:29,900
我觉得你…
I think you're, uh...

844
00:49:31,560 --> 00:49:33,070
我觉得你很棒
I think you're great.

845
00:49:33,790 --> 00:49:34,520
谢谢
Thanks.

846
00:49:43,210 --> 00:49:44,270
你在干嘛？
What are you doing?

847
00:49:44,590 --> 00:49:45,960
额 没什么
Uh, oh, nothing!

848
00:49:47,020 --> 00:49:47,670
我在做伸展运动
I'm stretching.

849
00:49:47,710 --> 00:49:49,840
嗯没错 再做一个
Yeah, gotta...Ooh, gotta get that one!

850
00:49:49,920 --> 00:49:52,320
嗯…我觉得我是时候走了
OK! Yeah, it's best I leave.

851
00:49:54,010 --> 00:49:56,480
蠢透了，蠢透了，蠢透了
Stupid, stupid, stupid!

852
00:49:56,590 --> 00:49:57,980
嘿 维克多
Hey, Victor!

853
00:49:58,200 --> 00:49:58,960
怎么了
Uh-huh?

854
00:49:59,920 --> 00:50:02,990
我今天玩得很开心
I had the best time.

855
00:50:03,160 --> 00:50:05,910
谢谢你 晚安 菲丽西
Thanks! Goodnight, Felicie.

856
00:50:06,080 --> 00:50:09,980
哦 抱歉 是尊贵的卡米尔小姐
Oh, sorry. Mademoiselle Camille Le Haut.

857
00:50:30,330 --> 00:50:31,290
真是可怜
Wretch!

858
00:50:31,440 --> 00:50:33,470
我要把她送进监狱
I want her put in prison!

859
00:50:34,030 --> 00:50:38,430
她偷了我的生活 我的荣耀 我的名字
She stole my life, my honour and my name!

860
00:50:38,560 --> 00:50:40,190
现在我要夺回来
I want it back!

861
00:50:42,590 --> 00:50:43,420
有点过了
Too much.

862
00:50:43,660 --> 00:50:44,040
我知道了
OK.

863
00:50:45,340 --> 00:50:47,070
你叫什么名字
What is your name?

864
00:50:51,960 --> 00:50:53,870
我叫菲丽西
My name is Felicie Lebras.

865
00:50:54,510 --> 00:50:56,860
我来自布列塔尼地区的一个孤儿院
I come from an orphanage in Brittany.

866
00:50:57,630 --> 00:50:59,130
我并不是故意冒充卡米尔的
I didn't mean to hurt Camille.

867
00:50:59,130 --> 00:51:01,280
我只是想在这儿…
I just wanted to be at the Opera and...

868
00:51:01,800 --> 00:51:02,810
对不起
I'm sorry.

869
00:51:03,850 --> 00:51:05,290
夫人
Madame...

870
00:51:07,000 --> 00:51:09,530
你这个叛徒
You traitor!

871
00:51:10,760 --> 00:51:12,200
你竟然知道这件事
You knew this!

872
00:51:12,700 --> 00:51:15,000
原来是你在背后捅刀子
You stabbed me in the back!

873
00:51:15,080 --> 00:51:16,240
你会被开除的
You are sacked!

874
00:51:16,270 --> 00:51:17,000
不要吵了
Silence!

875
00:51:19,070 --> 00:51:22,320
好了 不喜欢就憋着 这儿我说了算
Alright, like it or lump it, here is my deal.

876
00:51:22,350 --> 00:51:23,240
勒奥女士
Miss Le Haut,

877
00:51:23,850 --> 00:51:26,870
卡米尔明天可以进班练习
you may enter the coryphée class starting tomorrow.

878
00:51:27,450 --> 00:51:30,250
也可以参加《胡桃夹子》的试镜
And you will also be in the auditions for the part in 'The Nutcracker'.

879
00:51:31,160 --> 00:51:32,360
但是我得说清楚
But I want to be clear,

880
00:51:32,510 --> 00:51:35,500
如果你解雇奥黛特女士 我就解雇卡米尔
if you sack Madame Odette, I will sack Camille.

881
00:51:35,920 --> 00:51:36,490
你！
You!

882
00:51:37,290 --> 00:51:40,250
你给这个班开了个坏头
You made a terrible start to the classes,

883
00:51:40,620 --> 00:51:43,390
你已经欺骗了我们
and you have lied and cheated to be here.

884
00:51:44,650 --> 00:51:48,270
但你同时也做了很好的承诺
But you have also shown great promise,

885
00:51:48,970 --> 00:51:51,420
你也很努力的奉献了那么多
and you've worked hard and shown your dedication.

886
00:51:52,040 --> 00:51:53,850
你应该有一个好老师才行
You must have a good teacher.

887
00:51:55,160 --> 00:51:57,370
所以你也可以来试镜
So you may also stay in the auditions.

888
00:51:57,420 --> 00:51:59,760
如果你能公平公正的成功试镜
If you get the part in 'The Nutcracker' fair and square,

889
00:51:59,800 --> 00:52:01,240
你也可以拥有一个芭蕾舞的重要角色
you may become a coryphée too.

890
00:52:01,870 --> 00:52:04,800
如果你失败了 那你必须离开
If you fail to get the part, then you must leave the Opera.

891
00:52:04,830 --> 00:52:05,360
明白了吗
Is that clear?

892
00:52:05,930 --> 00:52:06,460
明白了
Yes.

893
00:52:07,260 --> 00:52:09,150
你也听清楚了吗 女士
Is that also clear to you, madame?

894
00:52:09,820 --> 00:52:10,790
清楚了
Clear.

895
00:52:11,160 --> 00:52:14,000
来自孤儿院的菲丽西
Then, Felicie Lebras from Brittany,

896
00:52:14,510 --> 00:52:17,700
你的未来掌握在你的手里
your future at the Opera is in your hands.

897
00:52:24,360 --> 00:52:25,020
哼
Hmm!

898
00:52:28,220 --> 00:52:29,870
要是她做到了怎么办 妈妈？
What if she's good, Mother?

899
00:52:29,900 --> 00:52:32,210
你必须夺得那个角色 懂了吗
Get that part, do you hear me?

900
00:52:32,840 --> 00:52:34,040
我要复仇
I want vengeance.

901
00:52:35,400 --> 00:52:36,730
把属于我的东西夺回来
I will have it.

902
00:52:48,290 --> 00:52:50,750
她连扫地都那么优雅
She even makes sweeping look graceful.

903
00:52:51,180 --> 00:52:52,920
她是个很好的舞者 不是吗
She was a good dancer, wasn't she?

904
00:52:52,940 --> 00:52:55,930
她不只是一个很好的舞者 她是这一代最好的舞者
Not just a good dancer. The best of her generation.

905
00:52:56,680 --> 00:52:58,810
她是舞台上的一团火
And then there was a fire onstage.

906
00:53:05,540 --> 00:53:06,410
哦
Oh!

907
00:53:07,290 --> 00:53:08,670
这是为什么
What's this for?

908
00:53:10,290 --> 00:53:11,550
为你所做的一切
For everything!

909
00:53:14,110 --> 00:53:15,680
我们可没时间做这些
We don't have time for this.

910
00:53:16,280 --> 00:53:18,080
我们得考虑你的未来
We're talking about your future now.

911
00:53:18,410 --> 00:53:21,150
你只有一个对手 卡米尔
You have only one opponent  Camille.

912
00:53:24,750 --> 00:53:27,170
我见过她跳舞 我知道
I have seen her.I know her.

913
00:53:28,750 --> 00:53:30,220
她的舞技堪称完美
Her technique is perfect,

914
00:53:30,400 --> 00:53:32,280
而且她比我们所看到的还要厉害
and she is stronger than she looks.

915
00:53:32,840 --> 00:53:34,970
她精准而又敏锐
She is precise, she is sharp,

916
00:53:35,230 --> 00:53:37,520
她的字典里没有“输”这个字
and losing is not a word in her vocabulary.

917
00:53:37,920 --> 00:53:40,110
上，下，上，下
Up, down! Up, down!

918
00:53:40,140 --> 00:53:41,610
上，下 再来一次
Up, down! Again!

919
00:53:41,660 --> 00:53:43,000
上，下
Up, down!

920
00:53:43,040 --> 00:53:44,240
我累了
I'm tired.

921
00:53:44,570 --> 00:53:46,250
“累”只属于失败者
'Tired' is for losers!

922
00:53:46,280 --> 00:53:49,360
再来一次 我一定要夺得那个角色
Again! I am going to get that part!

923
00:53:49,850 --> 00:53:53,360
如果你想和她正面对决 那你现在就输定了
If you try to take her down on her turf, you will fail.

924
00:53:53,840 --> 00:53:56,530
你吃得少 营养跟不上
Your diet suffers from eating very little food.

925
00:53:56,670 --> 00:53:58,710
肌肉就没有爆发力
Your muscles are like marshmallows.

926
00:53:59,200 --> 00:54:02,570
就目前而言 理论上你很难取胜
In short, on paper, you're going to get humiliated.

927
00:54:05,120 --> 00:54:08,520
真会安慰人 那我凭什么去赢她啊？
Great pep talk! So, how do I get that part?

928
00:54:08,840 --> 00:54:13,320
你能行 你拥有她梦寐以求的一片拼图
You get the part because you have something she can only dream of

929
00:54:13,610 --> 00:54:14,520
那就是热情
passion!

930
00:54:22,940 --> 00:54:24,300
以它为基础
Build on this.

931
00:54:24,620 --> 00:54:28,410
感受愤怒 欢快 悲伤
Feel your anger and your pain and your sorrow and your joy,

932
00:54:28,440 --> 00:54:30,410
将它尽情融入进你的舞蹈中
and put it all into your dance.

933
00:54:30,680 --> 00:54:32,800
感受音乐的生命力
Live the music, feel it.

934
00:54:35,820 --> 00:54:39,160
每个音符 每段旋律 每首曲子
Every note, every sound, every harmony

935
00:54:39,200 --> 00:54:41,260
都会带动你的身心随之起舞
needs to have your body vibrating

936
00:54:41,280 --> 00:54:45,050
都会带动你的身心随之起舞
from the end of your hair to the tips of your toes.

937
00:54:45,690 --> 00:54:50,540
到那时 只有到那时 你才有资格胜过她
And then, and only then, will you take her down.

938
00:54:59,820 --> 00:55:02,520
好了 今天要离开的人是
Alright! The person leaving us today is...

939
00:55:09,850 --> 00:55:10,970
嗯～～～
Ahem!

940
00:55:14,620 --> 00:55:14,960
哼
Hmm!

941
00:55:16,650 --> 00:55:18,800
诺拉小姐 这条路你走到头了
This is the end of the road, Miss Nora.

942
00:55:18,840 --> 00:55:24,680
什么路 哦 我被淘汰了 加油 打败她
What road? Oh, I'm finished. I like you. Beat her.

943
00:55:25,880 --> 00:55:28,730
卡米尔和菲丽西 明早八点
Camille and Felicie, tomorrow morning at 8:00am,

944
00:55:28,760 --> 00:55:30,480
我们就会知道你们中的哪一位
we will know which one of you will have the honour

945
00:55:30,510 --> 00:55:32,840
将会成为克拉拉 与罗西塔莫里一起出演胡桃夹子
of dancing Clara in 'The Nutcracker' with Rosita.

946
00:55:34,540 --> 00:55:38,490
希望明天你们可以展现最好的水准
I can only advise you to give everything, ladies.

947
00:55:39,480 --> 00:55:42,110
你的确进步了不少 脏兮兮的小耗子
You've made lots of progress, dirty, little rat,

948
00:55:42,270 --> 00:55:45,040
但明天他们绝对会选我
but tomorrow I am going to be the chosen one.

949
00:55:45,520 --> 00:55:46,130
我看未必
We'll see.

950
00:55:46,460 --> 00:55:50,060
那就放马过来 你整夜练习都没关系
You can work as hard as you like, you can train 24 hours a day,

951
00:55:50,270 --> 00:55:52,420
你永远什么都不是
but you will always be nothing!

952
00:55:52,830 --> 00:55:53,800
我是有身份的人
 I am somebody.

953
00:55:54,120 --> 00:55:57,530
有身份是吗 那请你告诉我 你有什么身份
Who exactly? Answer me! Who are you?

954
00:56:00,220 --> 00:56:01,070
你一无是处
You're nothing!

955
00:56:05,390 --> 00:56:06,770
就是个冒名顶替的小耗子
Nothing!

956
00:56:09,130 --> 00:56:10,160
是她错了 知道吗
She's wrong, you know.

957
00:56:10,750 --> 00:56:11,800
你并不孤单
You're not alone.

958
00:56:11,850 --> 00:56:12,240
什么
What?

959
00:56:15,040 --> 00:56:15,900
你还有我呢
You have me.

960
00:56:17,160 --> 00:56:19,390
我们今晚需要做点什么
And I know exactly what we are going to do.

961
00:56:19,530 --> 00:56:21,320
来证明我们心有灵犀
Tonight, to prove our connection,

962
00:56:21,360 --> 00:56:24,380
那就是一场浪漫的约会
we will embark on a little romantic party.

963
00:56:24,430 --> 00:56:31,120
我们今晚七点 一起登上埃菲尔铁塔观看烟花
I offer you the Eiffel Tower. I offer you fireworks. Tonight, 7:00pm

964
00:56:31,210 --> 00:56:32,000
不行 我还得练习呢
I should train.

965
00:56:32,040 --> 00:56:33,950
你不用练习
You don't need to train.

966
00:56:33,980 --> 00:56:35,480
更不用在意你的身份
You don't need to know who you are.

967
00:56:35,830 --> 00:56:37,740
你是独一无二的
You are unique.

968
00:56:38,080 --> 00:56:39,310
再说一次给我听
Say that again?

969
00:56:40,590 --> 00:56:41,130
晚上见
Tonight.

970
00:56:41,930 --> 00:56:46,320
菲丽西 我郑重其事地把它送给你
Felicie, it gives me great pleasure to present to you...

971
00:56:46,580 --> 00:56:48,160
哦不对
No!

972
00:56:53,370 --> 00:56:55,580
维克多 我进了最后一轮选拔
Victor! I'm in the final audition!

973
00:56:55,600 --> 00:56:57,660
真的吗 恭喜啊
Wow! Congratulations!

974
00:56:57,760 --> 00:57:00,840
我也有个好消息 老板终于和我说话了
I have great news too. My boss finally spoke to me!

975
00:57:00,910 --> 00:57:04,480
他说“别再踩我的脚了 你这个讨人厌的小怪胎”
He said, "Get off my foot, you biological mutation!"

976
00:57:05,820 --> 00:57:07,660
是不是挺好
That's good, right?

977
00:57:08,780 --> 00:57:11,130
呃 你可真没品味
Ugh! You have no class.

978
00:57:11,150 --> 00:57:13,440
你怎么就知道我没品味
What, me? No class?

979
00:57:13,450 --> 00:57:14,730
鲁迪就有品位
Rudi has class.

980
00:57:15,020 --> 00:57:16,270
又是他
Rudi again?

981
00:57:16,490 --> 00:57:18,670
怎么 他现在是你的男朋友了吗
What, is he your boyfriend now?

982
00:57:18,730 --> 00:57:22,990
不 但我们…心有灵犀
No! He and I, we're connected.

983
00:57:23,040 --> 00:57:28,840
好好好 我给你品味 还有你要的心有灵犀
OK, OK. You win! I'll give you class and connectivity-ness.

984
00:57:29,290 --> 00:57:30,510
我约你吃晚餐
Dinner! You and me.

985
00:57:30,540 --> 00:57:33,260
我们手持刀啊叉啊 还有餐巾纸什么的
Some knives and forks, napkins.

986
00:57:33,260 --> 00:57:36,640
就今晚七点 埃菲尔铁塔北侧
Uh, 7:00pm, north leg of the Eiffel Tower.

987
00:57:38,780 --> 00:57:39,660
这就算答应了吗
Is that a yes?

988
00:57:42,540 --> 00:57:45,390
是啊 她肯定答应了
Yeah. That's a yes.

989
00:57:46,590 --> 00:57:48,620
坐 我给你看个宝贝
Sit! I've got something for you.

990
00:57:51,900 --> 00:57:54,830
这是我以前的舞鞋 现在它属于你了
They were mine. Now they're yours.

991
00:57:55,180 --> 00:57:57,800
哇哦 谢谢
Wow! Thanks.

992
00:57:57,840 --> 00:58:01,210
不用谢 快吃饭吧 然后我们去训练
OK, enough talking. Eat, and then we practice for tomorrow.

993
00:58:03,040 --> 00:58:03,340
怎么了？
What?

994
00:58:04,160 --> 00:58:07,000
呃 鲁迪约我出去
Well, I'm going out with Rudi.

995
00:58:08,140 --> 00:58:11,240
他说我是独一无二的 没必要再练习了
He says I'm ready. He says I'm unique.

996
00:58:12,680 --> 00:58:14,080
你为什么要跳舞呢
Why do you dance?

997
00:58:14,590 --> 00:58:16,490
别问了好吗
Stop asking me that question!

998
00:58:17,080 --> 00:58:21,950
我还是舞蹈演员的时候 在演出之前训练也从不间断
When I was a dancer, the night before an audition, I trained and then I rested.

999
00:58:22,360 --> 00:58:23,710
鲁迪还在等我呢
Rudi's waiting for me.

1000
00:58:23,770 --> 00:58:24,200
别去了
Stay!

1001
00:58:24,300 --> 00:58:26,120
才不要 你又不是我妈妈
No! You're not my mom!

1002
00:58:27,630 --> 00:58:29,120
对不起
I'm sorry. I wasn't thinking.

1003
00:58:29,290 --> 00:58:31,000
算了 你去吧
OK. Go, then.

1004
00:58:56,030 --> 00:58:57,090
你看看那飞鸟
Look at the bird.

1005
00:58:57,250 --> 00:58:58,060
额…
Um...

1006
00:58:58,090 --> 00:58:59,770
再看看我
Now Look at me.

1007
00:59:00,060 --> 00:59:01,260
看那飞鸟
Look at the bird.

1008
00:59:01,260 --> 00:59:03,840
不 再看看我
No! Hmm? Look at me.

1009
00:59:04,040 --> 00:59:06,410
这是我特意为你写的一首诗
This is a poem I composed in your honour.

1010
00:59:06,540 --> 00:59:09,160
噢 当然了 一首诗
Ah, of course, a poem.

1011
00:59:09,520 --> 00:59:13,710
看啊 那飞鸟 翱翔于云天之上
"Look at the bird! He flies in the sky.“

1012
00:59:13,820 --> 00:59:15,150
来去无踪 身心自由
"No-one can trap him."

1013
00:59:15,280 --> 00:59:21,450
咕 咕咕 咕咕咕
 Coco-co-cocococo

1014
00:59:21,660 --> 00:59:22,380
你喜欢吗
Do you like?

1015
00:59:23,550 --> 00:59:27,120
这首诗 是挺特别的…
That's, uh...well, original.

1016
00:59:27,280 --> 00:59:30,300
我就知道你会喜欢 来吧 小美人 我们走
I know. Thank you. Come on, Minoushka!

1017
00:59:30,310 --> 00:59:33,660
去塔顶摘星星咯
Let us go to the very top! To the stars!

1018
00:59:34,140 --> 00:59:36,510
好了 马汀 我们排练一遍
OK, Matty, we practise.

1019
00:59:36,750 --> 00:59:39,320
音乐起 古典音乐
Music, please! Classical!

1020
00:59:39,500 --> 00:59:43,920
好吧 可我不怎么擅长古典音乐
OK, but that's not my musical comfort zone.

1021
00:59:44,920 --> 00:59:47,440
喔 快停下 不行不行
Oh, stop! Stop, stop, stop!

1022
00:59:47,710 --> 00:59:51,160
还是乡村音乐吧 不过要轻柔浪漫
We'll go Breton, but soft and romantic.

1023
00:59:51,200 --> 00:59:52,720
一定要震撼到她
This will blow her away.

1024
00:59:52,880 --> 00:59:55,440
等她来了 一定喜出望外
She arrives, she giggles.

1025
00:59:55,480 --> 00:59:59,420
而我则深沉又神秘地拿出音乐盒
I am looking dark and mysterious. I give her the music box.

1026
00:59:59,580 --> 01:00:03,530
她一定会这样 哦～人家好感动啊～
She's... "Oh! Oh!" Overwhelmed!

1027
01:00:03,530 --> 01:00:06,400
我不是很了解女孩子
Uh, I don't know much about girls.

1028
01:00:06,760 --> 01:00:09,000
应该说我完全搞不懂她们
Frankly, they are a mystery to me.

1029
01:00:09,130 --> 01:00:12,010
但我很确定她今晚不会来了
But I do know that this one's not coming.

1030
01:00:12,380 --> 01:00:15,660
你还太小还不明白 她一定会来的
Young, innocent fool! Of course she will come!

1031
01:00:16,960 --> 01:00:18,780
我已经闻到了她的香水味
I can already smell her perfume.

1032
01:00:24,340 --> 01:00:26,160
哦 不
Oh, no!

1033
01:00:26,200 --> 01:00:28,000
是乞丐啊 恶！
Oh, beggars! Ugh!

1034
01:00:28,170 --> 01:00:31,200
巴黎怎么到处都是这种人 恶心
Paris is infested with beggars! Yuck!

1035
01:00:31,740 --> 01:00:31,960
但是…
But...

1036
01:00:32,000 --> 01:00:32,580
别害怕
Don't be afraid.

1037
01:00:32,580 --> 01:00:32,910
但我…
But...

1038
01:00:32,920 --> 01:00:34,570
你别说话
Quiet! Follow me.

1039
01:00:34,800 --> 01:00:40,680
我根据哥萨克舞蹈中的动作 自创了一套拳法
Have no fear, I have developed a fighting technique based on Cossack dancing.

1040
01:00:40,760 --> 01:00:42,250
你别胡闹了
Don't be ridiculous!

1041
01:00:45,550 --> 01:00:48,460
好了 够了 听我说 他是我的朋友
OK, stop right there! He's my friend!

1042
01:00:48,460 --> 01:00:50,590
你在开玩笑么
Oh, is this some kind of joke?

1043
01:00:50,650 --> 01:00:53,200
不 他叫维克多 我们从小就认识
No! This is Victor. We grew up together.

1044
01:00:53,240 --> 01:00:55,630
天呐 你成功逗笑了我
Oh, my! This is funny.

1045
01:00:55,790 --> 01:00:56,670
朋友 哈？
Friends, huh?

1046
01:00:56,830 --> 01:00:59,240
只是朋友的话 你怎么一脸羞愧
If we're friends, why are you looking so ashamed?

1047
01:00:59,410 --> 01:01:00,990
我没有一脸羞愧啊
I'm not looking ashamed.

1048
01:01:01,230 --> 01:01:05,200
明明就有 你真让我失望 菲丽西
Oh, yes, you are! I feel sorry for you, Felicie.

1049
01:01:06,480 --> 01:01:08,300
哦 你在妒忌
Oh! You're jealous.

1050
01:01:08,520 --> 01:01:12,490
才没有 你进巴黎歌剧院到底想干嘛
No! Ever since you started at the Opera, who are you trying to be?

1051
01:01:12,880 --> 01:01:16,540
就为了和这个一身毛的大蒜苗鬼混吗
Mixing with this big, hairy asparagus?

1052
01:01:17,210 --> 01:01:18,140
你真可悲
You're so sad.

1053
01:01:18,350 --> 01:01:20,170
喔喔喔 矮矬穷
Whoa, whoa, whoa!

1054
01:01:20,380 --> 01:01:24,300
我只要动动手指就能把你打晕
I could knock you out with one flick of my tiny finger,

1055
01:01:24,460 --> 01:01:28,250
可这样会弄脏我的手指 洗都洗不干净
but that would make my finger dirty and smelly.

1056
01:01:28,430 --> 01:01:32,730
我是很脏没错 可是我从来不穿娘炮才穿的紧身裤
So, I'm dirty, but at least I don't spend my day in tights!

1057
01:01:33,070 --> 01:01:34,800
你们不要闹了
I can't believe this!

1058
01:01:34,880 --> 01:01:36,380
她是我的女神
She is my muse.

1059
01:01:36,430 --> 01:01:39,710
是吗 那她也是我的女神
Yeah, well, she is my whatever-you-just-said, too,

1060
01:01:39,760 --> 01:01:41,700
我们先认识的 你这个大蒜苗
with knobs on, asparagus!

1061
01:01:46,280 --> 01:01:46,800
住手
Stop!

1062
01:01:48,940 --> 01:01:50,540
你们两个白痴
You're both idiots!

1063
01:01:55,050 --> 01:01:58,120
好吧 那再会了
OK. Well, goodbye, then.

1064
01:02:00,140 --> 01:02:01,180
再见
Well, goodbye.

1065
01:02:04,520 --> 01:02:07,210
这招可真够阴险的
That is so low!

1066
01:03:05,130 --> 01:03:06,800
噢 糟了 最后一轮选拔
Oh, no! The audition!

1067
01:03:12,860 --> 01:03:14,680
我敢保证这次的…
I'm sure this...

1068
01:03:14,720 --> 01:03:15,580
看着点儿
Watch it!

1069
01:03:15,870 --> 01:03:18,540
《胡桃夹子》的演出肯定…
..production of 'Nutcracker' is going to...

1070
01:03:18,540 --> 01:03:19,150
借过
Excuse me!

1071
01:03:24,920 --> 01:03:25,740
嘿
Hey!

1072
01:03:33,000 --> 01:03:35,560
好极了 堪称完美
Bravo! Bravo!

1073
01:03:35,580 --> 01:03:37,160
谢谢你的表演 卡米尔小姐
Thank you, mademoiselle.

1074
01:03:37,530 --> 01:03:40,000
那位还没来 看来没必要再比了
The orphan is late. It's over.

1075
01:03:40,600 --> 01:03:44,860
好吧 既然菲丽西不想来
Well, as Felicie did not deign to show up for the audition,

1076
01:03:45,040 --> 01:03:47,420
那么就让卡米尔和罗西塔一同登台
it is Camille who will dance with Rosita.

1077
01:03:47,440 --> 01:03:49,440
等等 等等 请等一下 我来了
Wait! Wait! I'm here!

1078
01:03:50,170 --> 01:03:52,080
求求您 让我跳吧
Please, please let me dance.

1079
01:03:52,140 --> 01:03:54,410
已经太迟了 你不懂规矩吗
It's over! Don't you understand?

1080
01:03:54,440 --> 01:03:56,270
请您 坐下
Sit down!

1081
01:03:57,450 --> 01:03:59,040
我…我很抱歉
I-I apologise.

1082
01:03:59,290 --> 01:04:00,220
你睡过头了？
Did you sleep?

1083
01:04:01,210 --> 01:04:02,250
也不是
Not much.

1084
01:04:03,500 --> 01:04:04,740
那昨晚训练了吗
Did you train yesterday?

1085
01:04:05,260 --> 01:04:05,900
没有
No.

1086
01:04:06,330 --> 01:04:07,020
为什么
Why?

1087
01:04:12,000 --> 01:04:13,340
音乐 起
Alright, music!

1088
01:04:24,060 --> 01:04:24,540
哼
Hmm!

1089
01:04:31,440 --> 01:04:32,680
再来一遍
Start again.

1090
01:04:32,720 --> 01:04:34,700
这不合规矩
She fell! She's eliminated!

1091
01:04:34,800 --> 01:04:36,670
我说 再来一遍
Start again!

1092
01:04:51,100 --> 01:04:52,590
我们有言在先
You remember our deal?

1093
01:04:54,810 --> 01:04:58,990
卡米尔 《胡桃夹子》中的克拉拉由你出演
Camille, you will have the honour of dancing Clara in 'The Nutcracker'.

1094
01:05:11,950 --> 01:05:14,650
你以为这样就算完了吗 小耗子
Did you think it would end here, little rat?

1095
01:05:14,700 --> 01:05:19,280
不 放开我 不要
No! Let me go! No!

1096
01:05:19,340 --> 01:05:20,090
哦 不
Oh, no!

1097
01:05:22,880 --> 01:05:25,740
别走 别走
Please! Please!

1098
01:05:25,880 --> 01:05:28,330
奥黛特 不
Odette! No!

1099
01:05:29,280 --> 01:05:29,950
奥黛特
Odette!

1100
01:05:30,460 --> 01:05:31,290
菲丽西
Felicie!

1101
01:05:32,080 --> 01:05:34,240
真可怜 你们再也没法见面了吧
You will never see her again.

1102
01:05:35,790 --> 01:05:37,660
当然 你也该走人了
And, of course, you're sacked.

1103
01:05:58,540 --> 01:05:59,450
立正
Stop!

1104
01:06:00,940 --> 01:06:04,090
菲丽西这次又去哪儿了
Where is Felicie?

1105
01:06:04,600 --> 01:06:05,400
咳
Ahem!

1106
01:06:09,450 --> 01:06:10,300
我在这儿
I'm here.

1107
01:06:11,230 --> 01:06:14,840
喔 哦 好吧 很好
Oh! Well, uh, good.

1108
01:06:35,900 --> 01:06:37,160
看她的样子好像丢了魂一样
She's lost her spirit.

1109
01:06:37,200 --> 01:06:41,130
得得得 打起精神来 你帮过什么忙
Tut-tut-tut! Pull yourself together, you big fool!

1110
01:06:49,360 --> 01:06:52,670
我知道你在想维克多去哪儿了 我也很想他
I know. I miss him too.

1111
01:07:36,960 --> 01:07:41,200
♫ 你是否已经敞开心扉 我有些秘密想要透露 ♫
♪ Have you told me all? I've got things to say ♪

1112
01:07:41,900 --> 01:07:43,740
♫ 嘿 听得到吗 ♫
♪ Hey, I'm talking to you ♪

1113
01:07:43,800 --> 01:07:48,140
♫ 我们本应该一起创造精彩 设想未来 ♫
♪ We got things to do We got plans to make ♪

1114
01:07:48,640 --> 01:07:54,570
♫ 多希望你能陪伴我身旁 ♫
